    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable daily driver for someone comfortable with a few cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and a few small door dings, while the interior has some visible wear on the driver's seat and carpet. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may soon require routine maintenance such as new brake pads and a suspension tune-up. It is a solid, functional car that offers reliable transportation for a buyer looking for a budget-friendly option.",
